<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
   <div rend="parallel">
    <p xml:id="Aink220-kilavi"> notumalar varaiviṉkaṇ tōḻi cevilikk aṟattoṭu niṉṟatu.   </p>
      <p xml:lang="en"> The confidante standing up with virtue at the [prospect of] marriage with a stranger. </p>
   </div>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink220">
<l>alaṅkumaḻai poḻinta vakaṉka ṇaruvi</l>
<l>yāṭukaḻai yaṭukkat tiḻitaru nāṭaṉ</l>
<l>peruvarai yaṉṉa tiruviṟal viyaṉmārpu</l>
<l>muyaṅkātu kaḻinta nāḷivaṇ</l>
<l>mayaṅkitaḻ maḻaikkaṇ kaliḻu maṉṉāy</l>
       </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Mother, </l>
<l>her raining eyes, with confused petals, will weep</l>
<l>in the days spent without embracing </l>
<l>the brilliant, victorious, wide chest, like a big mountain, </l>
<l>of the man from the land where widening waterfalls,    </l>
<l>poured forth by swaying clouds, </l>
<l>cascade down the slopes with dancing bamboos. </l>
 
 </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
